  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed front porch, single storey&amp;nbsp;side to rear extension with their&amp;nbsp;unsympathetic&amp;nbsp;design,&amp;nbsp;the installation and replacement of the&amp;nbsp;existing&amp;nbsp;windows with lack of sufficient justification and inappropriate window type, the removal of chimney due to the&amp;nbsp;obtrusive and unsympathetic appearance&amp;nbsp;would not relate well or harmonise with the design and appearance of the host dwelling . This would be to the detriment of the character and appearance of the host dwelling and the Pinnerwood Park Estate Conservation Area, and be contrary to the high-quality design aspirations of the National Planning Policy Framework (2023), policies D3 (D(1) and D(11)) and HC1 of The London Plan (2021), policy CS1.B of the Harrow Core Strategy (2012), policies DM1 and DM7 of the Harrow Development Management Policies Local Plan (2013), the adopted Supplementary Planning Document: Residential Design Guide (2010) and the Pinnerwood Park Conservation Area Management Strategy (2009).&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
